---
title: Bistro-Style Double Steak and Easy Béarnaise Sauce with Herby Potatoes and Caesar Salad
description: Crack open a bottle of your favourite beverage because this recipe is date night ready! We've paired this bistro classic with a creamy homemade Caesar salad and golden roasted potatoes tossed in parsley butter! A luxurious béarnaise sauce adds a touch of elegance.
